Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.35,0:00:06.74,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.76,0:00:08.85,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.87,0:00:16.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:26.54,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:29.96,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.98,0:00:35.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.52,0:00:41.72,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:48.73,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:53.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.25,0:00:55.31,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:03.33,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.58,0:01:13.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.03,0:01:16.21,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.23,0:01:21.76,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.78,0:01:27.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, let's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.99,0:01:35.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.04,0:01:39.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.17,0:01:41.77,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.79,0:01:46.13,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.15,0:01:48.83,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.85,0:01:50.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:52.21,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.23,0:01:53.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.89,0:01:55.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:57.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:01:58.96,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:00.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.59,0:02:01.74,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:06.00,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:08.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:12.56,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.58,0:02:14.98,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:19.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:21.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.49,0:02:25.88,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.90,0:02:33.85,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.87,0:02:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the \NGreat Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.52,0:02:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.67,0:02:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.87,0:02:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become \Nthe next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.39,0:03:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and \Nless able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.22,0:03:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way \Nto the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.22,0:03:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the \NGrand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Separated from the rest of the Straw Hats,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.85,0:03:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy has broken out of the great prison Impel Down
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.31,0:03:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and is headed to the Navy Headquarters in order to rescue his brother, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.41,0:03:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Special Retrospective Before Marineford! The Vow of the Brotherhood!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That must be Ace-san's Vivre Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.06,0:04:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard a lot about you from Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He told me that you two always used to run through the fields together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.45,0:04:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Ace and I were always together!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.39,0:04:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.21,0:04:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna beat you this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eating together...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.07,0:04:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sleeping together...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.80,0:04:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spending all your spare time honing your skills...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.50,0:04:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still far from defeating me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.95,0:05:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it used to be -
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.68,0:05:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace-san told me nostalgically.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.21,0:05:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace went out to sea 3 years before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.54,0:05:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hadn't even eaten the devil fruit at that time but I couldn't beat him even once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hadn't seen him after he left?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.18,0:05:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I saw him in Alabasta once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh! I guess my letting you escape was pretty much pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.34,0:05:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't seen you in a while, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.56,0:05:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This brings back memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just in these waters on minor business,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.17,0:05:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought I might look you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.88,0:05:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minor business?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a member of the Whitebeard Pirates now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.61,0:05:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whitebeard Pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.67,0:05:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the mark of the Whitebeard Pirates. It's my pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:06:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.05,0:06:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy. Won't you join the Whitebeard Pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your friends can come too, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.09,0:06:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.86,0:06:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured not. Just thought I'd ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.14,0:06:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whitebeard is the greatest pirate I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna help him to be King of the Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.62,0:06:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...And not you, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.92,0:06:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine! Then we'll just have to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.50,0:06:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.72,0:06:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who said I was joining you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.07,0:06:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace! Are you sure you won't join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.78,0:06:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm chasing a certain man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.97,0:06:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name's Blackbeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He used to be a member of the 2nd Division of the Whitebeard Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.98,0:06:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,one of my men.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he committed the worst possible sin on a pirate ship:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.56,0:06:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he killed a crewmember and jumped ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.63,0:07:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, as the commander, I gotta find and get rid of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.75,0:07:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to give this to you. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.25,0:07:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold onto it, always.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.51,0:07:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but that paper will lead us to one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.36,0:07:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I want it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Older brothers can't help worrying...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.60,0:07:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if their younger brother is weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.34,0:07:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that he'll be a handful
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.99,0:07:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but please look after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Are you leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.50,0:07:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! I'll see you at the top of the pirates' world!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.90,0:08:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blackbeard...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I met him before in Mock Town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.85,0:08:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, pops!\N--Hey, buddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--This cherry pie tastes extremely bad! Hm?\N--This cherry pie tastes extremely good! Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.25,0:08:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! Wanna fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you fighting about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.53,0:08:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a pirate?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.32,0:08:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the bounty for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,30 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,30 million? For you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.35,0:08:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be true! It's gotta be a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.68,0:08:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lying! That's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.60,0:08:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! They're gonna take Bellamy on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.82,0:08:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.44,0:08:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mister! We want to go to the sky island!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.10,0:08:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know anything about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.03,0:09:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said "sky island!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.86,0:09:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.99,0:09:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you got me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys believe in such an ancient legend... that there's an island in the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.94,0:09:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just which era are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. The era where pirates dream about things is over
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.55,0:09:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I see idiots chasing after dreams like that, I get disgusted!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.33,0:09:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.96,0:09:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take them on, no matter what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sky island exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.00,0:10:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The new era they're talking about is crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The era where pirates have dreams will be over, they say?! Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.15,0:10:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People's dreams... have no end!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.91,0:10:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still can't believe that somebody was able to beat Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.59,0:10:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.01,0:10:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Warlords and the Navy are gonna fight against the Whitebeards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.05,0:10:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?! What's gonna happen?! W-W-W-W-Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.51,0:11:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is too much to hear at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.36,0:11:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a foolish man! You don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.48,0:11:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must say, that was just a prediction.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the battle will probably happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The World Government has made a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whitebeard is a man who would never allow his mates to be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though they know this, they announced the public execution of...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.46,0:11:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Portgaz D. Ace, a great commander of Whitebeard's.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.71,0:11:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.99,0:11:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace... is gonna get executed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.62,0:11:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard a pirate called Blackbeard...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...became a Warlord by defeating "Fire Fist" Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.82,0:12:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace is my older brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.42,0:12:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.60,0:12:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna go and rescue Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I heard the news, I couldn't believe it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.64,0:12:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I didn't know that you already met Teech.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.20,0:12:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember that that's the way he talks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blackbeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.85,0:12:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.20,0:12:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Blackbeard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.12,0:12:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh yeah, I never gave you my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.66,0:12:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised, too, when I heard that you were the brother of my commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you want to be here? You're gonna miss it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.01,0:13:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your brother's public execution!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found out later that the former Warlord right there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.56,0:13:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Crocodile was defeated by you, Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.09,0:13:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, I was trying to take his place as a Warlord so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.42,0:13:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...killing you was the most effective way to show my ability to the Government!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But fate has saved you instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pay your respects at his grave!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it weren't for him, you'd be the one who...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.44,0:13:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...would've been killed, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy that he killed was...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.99,0:13:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...called Thatch--the commander of the 4th Division of the Whitebeards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a good-hearted man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.49,0:14:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to help good old Whitebeard whom I owe so much
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.12,0:14:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I often visited the ship at that time,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I didn't notice what Teech was up to!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.94,0:14:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.13,0:14:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace-san sailed out to sea alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the commander of the 2nd Division of the Whitebeards,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he needed to get rid of Teech!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.96,0:14:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To all soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.60,0:14:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Report to the gulf!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready for the public execution of Portgaz D. Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.33,0:14:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.81,0:14:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All soldiers, report to the gulf!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.78,0:15:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready to set sail! We've got a lot to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.83,0:15:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait, Teech!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace! Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.66,0:15:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit calling me "commander."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.20,0:15:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People who use that term usually respect others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't fool me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it. But let me say just one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.04,0:16:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace! Why don't you join my crew?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.18,0:16:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's dominate the world together! The way is all planned out
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whitebeard's reign is over! I'll become the next Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.57,0:16:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, I'm gonna kill Straw Hat Luffy who is in the Water Seven...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.36,0:16:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as a gift to the Government!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.94,0:16:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy? What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.35,0:16:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You know him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another reason I can't let you go free!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.65,0:16:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's my brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.36,0:16:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm not gonna become one of...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...your crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.55,0:17:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.43,0:17:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you want, Ace. You want to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.21,0:17:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder. Killing a crewmember is the worst crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.38,0:17:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I killed Thatch - the commander of the 4th Division!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.54,0:17:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the ship's rules, the one who finds it can eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.51,0:17:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remembered how they looked from seeing all the fruit in a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I noticed this was the one I'd been looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you killed Thatch? To steal it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.54,0:18:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it wasn't for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.45,0:18:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power chose me, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.97,0:18:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that fruit, I've become the world's strongest man, Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! This one is different from all the other Logia type.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace, your body is made out of fire, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine's made out of darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.82,0:18:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Firefly! Fiery Doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.54,0:18:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.86,0:18:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.65,0:18:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it was a Logia type fruit, you could fend off these attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.63,0:19:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you. Darkness will drag in everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bullets, blades, blows, fire, even thunder!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.08,0:19:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I can't fend off attacks like you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.75,0:19:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body will absorb even pain more than a normal person's.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.18,0:19:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, in return for these risks, there's another thing that my darkness drags in!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vortex!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.15,0:19:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The gravity of the darkness will pull in Devil Fruit eaters...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.54,0:19:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The gravity?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...And my body will...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's this? You get it already, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.39,0:20:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.06,0:20:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't been hit by somebody for long time, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that you got it when I grabbed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.31,0:20:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another thing that my darkness drags in is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.95,0:20:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Devil Fruit powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.23,0:20:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means as long as I touch them, Devil Fruit eaters can't use any of their powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.24,0:20:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Logia, Zoan, Paramecia...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.14,0:21:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the Devil Fruit eaters in this world who put too much confidence in their powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.71,0:21:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...can't protect themselves from my striking power!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.97,0:21:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I won't let you touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vortex!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.97,0:21:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,St. Elmo's Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.14,0:21:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.67,0:21:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing can compete against darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.53,0:21:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.60,0:21:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But your power is such a valuable one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.29,0:21:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace! You got to join my crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.46,0:21:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I yield to power, there's no point in being born a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.29,0:21:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never leave anything to be regretted later in my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.83,0:22:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand, stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.05,0:22:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This world is worthless if you can't survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.99,0:22:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a shame, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.86,0:22:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die in the darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.94,0:22:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Commandment!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.65,0:22:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Emperor!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.42,0:22:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun or the darkness - there'll be only one winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.36,0:22:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna make Whitebeard the king!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.42,0:23:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three hours before Ace's exectution at the Navy HQ,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.34,0:23:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all seven Warlords assemble and await Whitebeard's arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.58,0:23:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the same time, the three Admirals gather...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.71,0:23:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tension keeps rising before the inevitable battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.23,0:23:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.35,0:23:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Special Retrospective Before Marineford! The Three Navy Admirals Come Together!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.94,0:23:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
